queries.sql: SELECT *, `tbl_pegawai`.`pegawai_nip`, count(tbl_pegawai.pegawai_nip) as jumlahasn, concat(tbl_formasi.jabatan_kode, tbl_formasi.instansi_unor) as jabatan FROM `tbl_formasi` LEFT JOIN `tbl_jabatan` ON `tbl_formasi`.`jabatan_kode` = `tbl_jabatan`.`jabatan_kode` LEFT JOIN `tbl_unor` ON `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_unor` = `tbl_unor`.`instansi_unor` LEFT JOIN `tbl_pegawai` ON `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_unor` = `tbl_pegawai`.`instansi_unor` and `tbl_formasi`.`jabatan_kode` = `tbl_pegawai`.`jabatan_kode` WHERE `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_id` = 'A0' GROUP BY `jabatan` ORDER BY `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_unor` asc
